ного анализа и мониторинга показателей</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-testid="Spacer" class="Spacer_spacer_type_margin__zUd_5 Spacer_spacer_size_s9__gKJU_"></div><div class="sc-hvigdm oKHaL theme_static_theme__ImsJk theme_theme__En18D theme_theme_light__s_qYk"><div data-testid="Island" class="sc-dTvVRJ ekWJex"><div l="1,-1" class="sc-ggWZvA ctZOfy sc-hjsuWn bNmIJV"><div data-testid="CardEdge" class="Spacer_spacer_type_padding__5glfl Spacer_spacer_size_s9__gKJU_ sc-fhHczv bRuvZH"></div><div class="sc-jwTyAe dhchqm"><div class="sc-dTvVRJ tAkYp"><div l="2,-2" m="2,-2" sl="2,-2" sm="1,-1" class="sc-ggWZvA feyiJa"><h2 data-testid="H2" variant="title1" component="h2" class="sc-ipUnzB icfkXF Typography_variant_title1">Новости</h2></div></div><div data-testid="Spacer" class="Spacer_spacer_type_margin__zUd_5 Spacer_spacer_size_s9__gKJU_"></div><div class="BlogFeed_blogFeed__ja4AY" data-testid="BlogFeed"><div class="sc-dTvVRJ tAkYp"><div l="2,-2" sm="1,-1" class="sc-ggWZvA feyiJa"><div data-testid="AbstractFeed" class="sc-gXbNzB bflGcF"><div class="AbstractFeed__header"></div><div class="sc-VLMBG lnYeIX"><div class="FeedContentContainer__contentContainer"><div class="FeedContentContainer__content"><div></div><div class="sc-VLMBG lnYeIX"><div class="FeedContentContainer__contentContainer"><div class="FeedContentContainer__content"><div></div><div class="OneColumnGrid_oneColumnGrid__h3AOH" data-testid="OneColumnGrid"><div data-testid="NewsSection" class="sc-hqtLyI beFSxD"><div class="sc-iVnIWt kKeUeI CardContainer__background"></div><a class="sc-KsiuK hHrFHl CardContainer__content sc-kbeVdv jlxHxC NewsSection_hoverable" href="/adv/news/itogi-goda-ot-yandex-metrika" target="_self" rel=""><p class="sc-ipUnzB bTlBNx sc-cgHfjM zJHci NewsSection__date Typography_variant_title2" variant="title2" component="p">24 дек<br><mark>2025</mark></p><div class="NewsSection__body"><div class="NewsSection__hovarable"><div data-testid="NewsCard" class="sc-fFmWCW bzcvkm"><div class="NewsCard__content"><p variant="title2" component="p" class="sc-ipUnzB bTlBNx Typography_variant_title2">Итоги года от Яндекс Метрики: запуск Тег Менеджера, большое обновление интерфейса и новые дашборды</p><div data-testid="Spacer" class="Spacer_spacer_type_margin__zUd_5 Spacer_spacer_size_s4__sCmS1"></div><div variant="body" component="div" color="text_secondary_2" class="sc-ipUnzB isCLWE Typography_variant_body">В 2025 году мы совершенствовали интерфейс, расширяли возможности для аналитики заказов и управления ими, добавляли новые инструменты для поиска инсайтов и делали рекомендации более персонализированными. В дайджесте рассказываем подробно о самых больших обновлениях Метрики за год.</div></div><picture layout="full" class="sc-jYczwO kNtWMd NewsCard__image" itemscope="" itemType="http://schema.org/ImageObject" data-testid="Image"><img alt="" itemProp="contentUrl" loading="lazy" width="1" height="1" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="sc-fszimp jjmobf" style="color:transparent" sizes="(min-width: 1440px) 1920px, (min-width: 1280px) 1920px, (min-width: 800px) 1920px, (min-width: 600px) 828px, (min-width: 0px) 828px, 100vw" srcSet="/adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F114583%2F2a0000019b4b50e82a5492cf60af189071e5%2Forig&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F114583%2F2a0000019b4b50e82a5492cf60af189071e5%2Forig&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F114583%2F2a0000019b4b50e82a5492cf60af189071e5%2Forig&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F114583%2F2a0000019b4b50e82a5492cf60af189071e5%2Forig&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F114583%2F2a0000019b4b50e82a5492cf60af189071e5%2Forig&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F114583%2F2a0000019b4b50e82a5492cf60af189071e5%2Forig&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F114583%2F2a0000019b4b50e82a5492cf60af189071e5%2Forig&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F114583%2F2a0000019b4b50e82a5492cf60af189071e5%2Forig&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w" src="/adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F114583%2F2a0000019b4b50e82a5492cf60af189071e5%2Forig&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75"/></picture></div></div></div></a></div><div data-testid="NewsSection" class="sc-hqtLyI beFSxD"><div class="sc-iVnIWt kKeUeI CardContainer__background"></div><a class="sc-KsiuK hHrFHl CardContainer__content sc-kbeVdv jlxHxC NewsSection_hoverable" href="/adv/news/novye-instrumenty-v-yandex-teg-menedzhere" target="_self" rel=""><p class="sc-ipUnzB bTlBNx sc-cgHfjM zJHci NewsSection__date Typography_variant_title2" variant="title2" component="p">18 дек<br><mark>2025</mark></p><div class="NewsSection__body"><div class="NewsSection__hovarable"><div data-testid="NewsCard" class="sc-fFmWCW bzcvkm"><div class="NewsCard__content"><p variant="title2" component="p" class="sc-ipUnzB bTlBNx Typography_variant_title2">Новые инструменты в Яндекс Тег Менеджере</p><div data-testid="Spacer" class="Spacer_spacer_type_margin__zUd_5 Spacer_spacer_size_s4__sCmS1"></div><div variant="body" component="div" color="text_secondary_2" class="sc-ipUnzB isCLWE Typography_variant_body">Продолжаем улучшать Тег Менеджер: в этот раз добавили новые триггеры и переменные, сравнение версий контейнера и возможность создавать компоненты прямо из окна настройки тегов и триггеров.</div></div><picture layout="full" class="sc-jYczwO kNtWMd NewsCard__image" itemscope="" itemType="http://schema.org/ImageObject" data-testid="Image"><img alt="" itemProp="contentUrl" loading="lazy" width="1" height="1" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="sc-fszimp jjmobf" style="color:transparent" sizes="(min-width: 1440px) 1920px, (min-width: 1280px) 1920px, (min-width: 800px) 1920px, (min-width: 600px) 828px, (min-width: 0px) 828px, 100vw" srcSet="/adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F126209%2F2a0000019b30eb936c82672e8745af7defa4%2Forig&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F126209%2F2a0000019b30eb936c82672e8745af7defa4%2Forig&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F126209%2F2a0000019b30eb936c82672e8745af7defa4%2Forig&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F126209%2F2a0000019b30eb936c82672e8745af7defa4%2Forig&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F126209%2F2a0000019b30eb936c82672e8745af7defa4%2Forig&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F126209%2F2a0000019b30eb936c82672e8745af7defa4%2Forig&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F126209%2F2a0000019b30eb936c82672e8745af7defa4%2Forig&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F126209%2F2a0000019b30eb936c82672e8745af7defa4%2Forig&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w" src="/adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F126209%2F2a0000019b30eb936c82672e8745af7defa4%2Forig&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75"/></picture></div></div></div></a></div><div data-testid="NewsSection" class="sc-hqtLyI beFSxD"><div class="sc-iVnIWt kKeUeI CardContainer__background"></div><a class="sc-KsiuK hHrFHl CardContainer__content sc-kbeVdv jlxHxC NewsSection_hoverable" href="/adv/news/upravlyat-zakazami-teper-mozhno-pryamo-v-metrike" target="_self" rel=""><p class="sc-ipUnzB bTlBNx sc-cgHfjM zJHci NewsSection__date Typography_variant_title2" variant="title2" component="p">17 дек<br><mark>2025</mark></p><div class="NewsSection__body"><div class="NewsSection__hovarable"><div data-testid="NewsCard" class="sc-fFmWCW bzcvkm"><div class="NewsCard__content"><p variant="title2" component="p" class="sc-ipUnzB bTlBNx Typography_variant_title2">Встречайте управление заказами в Метрике — без интеграции с CRM и сложных настроек</p><div data-testid="Spacer" class="Spacer_spacer_type_margin__zUd_5 Spacer_spacer_size_s4__sCmS1"></div><div variant="body" component="div" color="text_secondary_2" class="sc-ipUnzB isCLWE Typography_variant_body">Добавили новый инструмент “Управление заказами”. Он позволяет связывать посещения сайта с заказами прямо в Метрике, без доработок и интеграции с CRM. Вы просто отмечаете, какие визиты привели к заказу, какой доход они принесли и на каком этапе сделки находятся — всё в привычном интерфейсе.</div></div><picture layout="full" class="sc-jYczwO kNtWMd NewsCard__image" itemscope="" itemType="http://schema.org/ImageObject" data-testid="Image"><img alt="" itemProp="contentUrl" loading="lazy" width="1" height="1" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="sc-fszimp jjmobf" style="color:transparent" sizes="(min-width: 1440px) 1920px, (min-width: 1280px) 1920px, (min-width: 800px) 1920px, (min-width: 600px) 828px, (min-width: 0px) 828px, 100vw" srcSet="/adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F95093%2F2a0000019b2aa12ff9f264a62f6e59185312%2Forig&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F95093%2F2a0000019b2aa12ff9f264a62f6e59185312%2Forig&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F95093%2F2a0000019b2aa12ff9f264a62f6e59185312%2Forig&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F95093%2F2a0000019b2aa12ff9f264a62f6e59185312%2Forig&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.mds.yandex.net%2Fget-adv%2F95093%2F2a0000019b2aa12ff9f264a62f6e59185312%2Forig&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /adv/_next/image?url=https%3A%2